{
  "id": "69d3b2b3f1e461443cf0fb0a",
  "title": "Mii",
  "created": 1775481601,
  "updated": 1775484579,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d3b2b3f1e461443cf0fb0a",
      "text": "Mii",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775481601,
      "updated": 1775481601
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b300000000000063bdce",
      "text": " [任天堂のゲーム機]の様々なソフト（ゲーム）で使うことができる[アバター]のこと",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775481601,
      "updated": 1775481647
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b32f000000000063bdd0",
      "text": " [Wii]で初登場して以降、様々なハードに搭載されている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775481647,
      "updated": 1775481683
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b3bd000000000063bdd2",
      "text": " 影は薄いが、何気に最新ハードである[Switch 2]までの主要ハード全てに搭載されている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775481789,
      "updated": 1775482775
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b431000000000063bdd3",
      "text": " \tSwitch 2の編集画面はSwitch 1と同じに見えるが、[ダークテーマ]や[マウス操作]に新たに対応している",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775481905,
      "updated": 1775481948
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b396000000000063bdd1",
      "text": " \tMiiの内蔵機能が無いDSにおける[トモダチコレクション]では、ソフト内にMiiを保存する",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775481751,
      "updated": 1775481981
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3be810000000000484dc2",
      "text": " \t\t時系列的に Wii から輸入されてるっぽい。おもろい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775484546,
      "updated": 1775484579
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b303000000000063bdcf",
      "text": "\tハードを追うにつれて、使えるパーツも増えている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775481604,
      "updated": 1775481998
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b7c1000000000063bdeb",
      "text": "\tその為かは不明だが、基本的に前世代ハードへの移行はできない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482817,
      "updated": 1775482913
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b822000000000063bded",
      "text": "\t\t同世代（Wii/DSやWii U/3DS）は相互に移行できる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482915,
      "updated": 1775482935
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b80b000000000063bdec",
      "text": "\t\t詳細：[Miiの引き継ぎ方法]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482891,
      "updated": 1775482900
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b492000000000063bdd5",
      "text": "\t一部ソフトでは、基本のMiiのパーツの他にも使えるパーツがある",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482002,
      "updated": 1775482103
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b4f5000000000063bdd6",
      "text": "\t\t[Miitopia]（Switch版）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482101,
      "updated": 1775482119
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b557000000000063bdd9",
      "text": "\t\t\thttps://www.nintendo.com/jp/switch/aw8sa/create/index.html",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482200,
      "updated": 1775482201
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b50c000000000063bdd7",
      "text": "\t\t\t[メイク]と[ウィッグ]が使える",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482125,
      "updated": 1775482133
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b541000000000063bdd8",
      "text": "\t\t\tメイクは重ね塗りができるので、そこそこ好き勝手できる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482178,
      "updated": 1775482239
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b57e000000000063bdda",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/69e765ad0b02deee003ff6e3e39ae2e3]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482239,
      "updated": 1775482253
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b58c000000000063bddc",
      "text": " \t\t\t\thttps://www.reddit.com/r/NintendoSwitch/comments/1jlw44g/nintendo_should_replace_the_builtin_mii_maker/?tl=ja",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482253,
      "updated": 1775482255
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b580000000000063bddb",
      "text": "\t\t[トモダチコレクション わくわく生活]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482241,
      "updated": 1775482323
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b5d3000000000063bdde",
      "text": "\t\t\t髪型は従来のセットパーツの他に、前髪と後髪で別のパーツを組み合わせることが可能",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482323,
      "updated": 1775482368
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b5ff000000000063bddf",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tただし[スキンヘッド]は他のパーツと併用不可",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482368,
      "updated": 1775482383
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b60e000000000063bde0",
      "text": "\t\t\t目は追加で以下のパーツが追加されている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482383,
      "updated": 1775482441
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b648000000000063bde1",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tまつ毛（上・下）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482441,
      "updated": 1775482456
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b657000000000063bde2",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t目のくぼみ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482456,
      "updated": 1775482460
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b65b000000000063bde3",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tサブカラーの上まつ毛",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482460,
      "updated": 1775482481
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b66b000000000063bde4",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t瞳の柄",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482476,
      "updated": 1775482511
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b69c000000000063bde5",
      "text": "\t\t\t耳の形も選択できる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482525,
      "updated": 1775482531
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b6a2000000000063bde6",
      "text": "\t\t\tメガネは[モノクル]型が追加されている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482531,
      "updated": 1775482565
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b6c4000000000063bde7",
      "text": "\t\t\t顔の皺やメイクもプリセットから選択可能",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482565,
      "updated": 1775482627
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b703000000000063bde8",
      "text": "\t\t\tフェイスペイントを使えば[マイデザイン]のように自由に絵を書ける",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482627,
      "updated": 1775482658
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b722000000000063bde9",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tただし平面なので既存の髪型も併用しないとハリボテ感が目立つ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482658,
      "updated": 1775482685
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b73c000000000063bdea",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t顔からはみ出すと裏側からお面のように見えてしまう",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775482685,
      "updated": 1775482715
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b482000000000063bdd4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775481987,
      "updated": 1775481987
    }
  ]
}